{
  "stem": "1530.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, his name-- well, later on, not then, but a couple of days later we found out that he was Mengele.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was the most important man there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had to say life or death.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His right arm meant life, his left was death.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know this until we arrived to the cells.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, but-- first he took out my older sister Tipi, Chicha, and Isabelle to the right.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, fast, fast, fast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the line-- I went with my mother, my little sister.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I guess my brother was with men, so I don't remember what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they-- they turned us around when I was with my mother and my little sister.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they turned us around, and they said--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mengele, because he didn't take out enough people to the right hand side, which we only knew retroactively, you know, that--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he pulled me out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- to the right hand side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Left, with my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think that I was put out there, even though I was young, I was busty, and I looked-- the Hungarian women looked healthy.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even I looked healthy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then when I saw him pull me out, I looked at my mother and my little sister.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said to Mengele, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My little sister.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "13.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let her go anyway, I said.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let her go with my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know they're going to their death.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my mother knew it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm sure of that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that hurts.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I will never get over that, never in my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To walk into your death.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not many people knew that, but my mother knew it from the Polish Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
